#: src/pages/ChatPage.tsx
msgid "60-second setup: create an Incoming Webhook in Slack (one channel, one URL) and paste it here. The agent gains exactly one ability — posting messages to that channel; it reads nothing from Slack. The URL stays in this tab's memory."
msgstr "60 秒完成设置:在 Slack 中创建一个 Incoming Webhook(一个频道、一个 URL),然后把 URL 粘贴到这里。助手只会获得一项能力 — 向该频道发消息;不会从 Slack 读取任何内容。URL 只保存在此标签页的内存中。"

#: src/pages/ChatPage.tsx
msgid "A hatchling travels as one .agent file: its playbook, starter files, and requested capabilities — never credentials or chat history. Importing always shows a preview first, and packaged instructions can never unlock more than you see there."
msgstr "一只小鸡仔以一个 .agent 文件的形式旅行:它的手册、初始文件和请求的能力 — 绝不包含凭据或聊天记录。导入时总是先显示预览,打包的指令永远无法解锁超出预览所示的内容。"

#: src/pages/ChatPage.tsx
msgid "A messy sample spreadsheet is ready — ask for a cleanup and watch every change land."
msgstr "一份乱糟糟的示例电子表格已准备就绪 — 让它帮忙整理,看每一处改动实时落地。"

#: src/pages/ChatPage.tsx
msgid "A structured, exportable record of this hatchling's runs — model turns, tool calls, and writes, with credentials always excluded. It stays in this tab until you export it."
msgstr "这只小鸡仔运行过程的结构化可导出记录 — 模型回合、工具调用和写入,始终不含凭据。在你导出之前,它只保存在此标签页中。"

